msgid "Privacy note:"
msgstr "Nota de privacidad:"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1121
msgid ""
"Jetonomy only sends oEmbed requests to Meta when a user pastes an "
"Instagram/Facebook URL. No tracking, no user data: just the public post URL "
"and your app token. Leave these fields blank to skip Instagram/Facebook "
"embeds entirely; the URL will render as a plain clickable link."
msgstr ""
"Jetonomy solo envía solicitudes de oEmbed a Meta cuando un usuario pega una "
"URL de Instagram/Facebook. Sin seguimiento, sin datos de usuario: solo la "
"URL del post público y tu token de aplicación. Déjalos en blanco para "
"omitir incrustraciones de Instagram/Facebook completamente; la URL se "
"renderizará como un enlace clickeable simple."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1129
#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1299
